    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "What an incredible opportunity! This vehicle is in truly mint condition \u2014 the paint is flawless and gleaming, the interior is immaculate with zero wear, and everything mechanical is in perfect working order. This is the kind of car you'd be proud to show off at any gathering, yet it's equally at home as a reliable daily driver. Don't miss your chance to own a vehicle that's as close to showroom-fresh as you'll find on the used market!",
