    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Looking for a project car or a budget-friendly fixer-upper? Here's your chance to get behind the wheel without breaking the bank! This vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it has seen better days and will require meaningful repairs and TLC to get back on the road reliably. Whether you're a DIY enthusiast, a mechanic looking for a weekend project, or someone who just needs a parts car, this could be exactly what you're after. Come take a look and see the potential for yourself \u2014 priced honestly and ready to go to a new home!",
      "price": 5000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Rare find alert \u2014 this one is truly exceptional! This vehicle is in mint condition, meaning it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every detail has been meticulously maintained: the paint gleams without a blemish, the interior is spotless and fresh, and the mechanicals are in outstanding shape. There's no catch here \u2014 this is simply one of those unicorn cars that has been loved and cared for at the highest level. If you want the very best without buying new, this is your car. Come see it in person \u2014 we're confident it will exceed your expectations!",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition \u2014 a solid, dependable car that has been well cared for over the years. The exterior presents nicely overall, with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use; no significant dents or structural damage to report. The paint retains good color and gloss in most areas, though you may notice slight fading in a spot or two upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with upholstery showing moderate wear on the high-contact areas but nothing torn or badly damaged. Mechanically, the car runs and drives confidently \u2014 the engine starts readily, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all major systems are in good working order. This is a practical, reliable vehicle that has plenty of life left in it, and represents a strong value for a buyer looking for dependable everyday transportation without paying mint-condition prices.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives, but buyers should go in with realistic expectations. The exterior shows visible wear including several scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading, though nothing that affects the structural integrity of the body. Inside, the cabin is functional but worn: the upholstery has seen better days with some staining and fraying, and a few interior trim pieces show age. Mechanically, the engine starts reliably and the car handles everyday driving adequately, though it may benefit from some maintenance attention in the near future \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting. This is a solid option for a buyer who needs dependable transportation and is comfortable with a vehicle that has some miles and wear on it, priced fairly to reflect its actual condition.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition and represents a dependable, well-cared-for used car at a fair price. The exterior presents nicely with only the minor scuffs and light scratches you'd expect from normal everyday use \u2014 no major dents, rust, or body damage to report. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and all major mechanical systems are functioning properly; routine maintenance has been kept up, and the car drives confidently on the road. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with normal wear on the seats and trim but nothing that detracts from the overall experience. The tires have good tread remaining, and the brakes are in solid working order. This is a honest, reliable vehicle that should serve its next owner well without requiring immediate significant repairs \u2014 a genuine good-condition buy.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    }
